    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i've heard about fractures and they usually involve a snap or something, i didnt hear anything like that. it just looks really puffy. i don't really have time to go to the clinic today, i have work. do u think it's really necessary to go in if i just keep it elevated and ice it for like 48 hours first? it'll probably just be a bad sprain.",
