    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems like a lot of trouble for something that might just be a sprain. i'm pretty sure the only real way to know is an x-ray, and i don't want to deal with the cost and the wait if it's just swelling. if i just take some ibuprofen and stick to the RICE method strictly, won't the inflammation go down enough that i can tell? i'm sure i'll be fine if i just rest it for a couple days.",
